result.execSummary:
The defendant David Alexander Diedrich-Mcfarlane was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. David Alexander Diedrich-Mcfarlane is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • David Alexander Diedrich-Mcfarlane was found guilty of Possess w/ Intent-THC(>200-1000g), a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(h)2.
  • David Alexander Diedrich-Mcfarlane was found guilty of Possess w/Intent-Cocaine (>1-5g), a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(cm)1r.
